  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "The Last Chancers Omnibus gathers 13th Legion, Kill Team, and Annihilation Squad, giving Colonel Schaeffer's penal regiment a full original arc: Ork-incursion attrition on Typhos Prime, a diplomatic-cover assassination among the Tau Empire, and a warp-shattered run to Armageddon to kill von Strab in Acheron. Lieutenant Kage's bitter memoir voice binds the trilogy, from condemned sergeant to sole survivor to haunted almost-psyker, always under Schaeffer's cold arithmetic of redemption through expendability. It is the natural entry point for the original Last Chancers shelf: dirty-mission military fiction with heist turns, command betrayal, and the grim question of whether survival is grace or merely being reused.",
